 A GLOBAL PLATFORM 


Europe & Asia Pacific: Learn more about Cantor’s worldwide presence
Cantor Fitzgerald has offices and trading desks in all major financial centers throughout the world. We possess one of the largest institutional sales forces serving over 5,000 clients worldwide in 33 locations. Through the acquisition of Seymour Pierce in London and Dolmen Stockbrokers in Ireland, we now have expanded presence in Europe and are serving clients from new offices in Dublin, Cork and Limerick.										

