Investment Banking

World-class service for leading growth enterprises.
Cantor Fitzgerald’s Investment Banking division focuses on providing capital raising and advisory services to growth oriented companies. The group's structuring and distribution capabilities are focused on addressing and providing innovative solutions to complex issues and challenges for clients across the globe. Our Investment Banking team specializes in tailoring efficient and cost-effective corporate finance solutions, from accessing the capital markets to restructuring balance sheets, seeking acquisition or disposition candidates, merchant banking and other value-added services. 


 










