Careers

Cantor Fitzgerald did not become a premier global financial services provider overnight. The company’s significant accomplishments are a direct result of continuously hard work by our solid team of dedicated individuals. As we continue to grow and expand across all business sectors we continuously seek talented candidates who can meet our demands for success. 

It’s an exciting time to work at Cantor Fitzgerald. If you are looking for a unique employment experience and are driven to achieve, then we want to discuss opportunities with you. 

Cantor Fitzgerald offers a competitive salary, comprehensive benefits package and a work environment characterized by an unwavering committment to professional growth. We are an equal opportunity employer. 

We are currently recruiting for a diversity of challenging positions.
Click here to find out about opportunities at Cantor. 

 

 







